        <title>ELECTRONIC ACCELERATOR PEDAL</title>
        <para>This feature eliminates the mechanical linkage used with conventional accelerator pedals. An accelerator
            position sensor within the accelerator pedal assembly provides the ECM with a signal representing the
            driver's demand for power.
